DESTROYED!

00:00:47.214 --> 00:00:49.650
HE WON!
YUGI WON!

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:53.887
All: YAY! WAY TO
GO, YUGI! YEAH!

00:00:53.887 --> 00:00:57.024
LET'S NOT FORGET.
THIS ISN'T OVER
UNTIL PEGASUS

