IT'S TIME
TO D-D-D-D-D-DUEL!

00:02:11.064 --> 00:02:13.600
[ECHOING]
♪ YU-GI-OH ♪

00:02:15.402 --> 00:02:17.671
Joey: DON'T WORRY, YUGI.
HE COULDN'T HAVE GOTTEN FAR.

00:02:17.671 --> 00:02:18.672
Yugi: WE'VE GOT
TO FIND HIM.

00:02:18.672 --> 00:02:20.040
PEGASUS IS
THE ONLY ONE

00:02:20.040 --> 00:02:21.341
WHO CAN RESTORE
GRANDPA'S SOUL!

00:02:21.341 --> 00:02:22.843
WAIT A MINUTE!

00:02:22.843 --> 00:02:24.544
All: HUH?

00:02:24.544 --> 00:02:25.779
WHY? WHAT'S
THE MATTER, TéA?

00:02:25.779 --> 00:02:28.081
THAT TOWER.
IT LOOKS...

00:02:28.081 --> 00:02:29.349
YEAH. GO ON.

00:02:29.349 --> 00:02:31.251
I THINK I'VE
BEEN THERE BEFORE

00:02:31.251 --> 00:02:33.520
WITH TRISTAN
AND BAKURA.
HUH?

00:02:33.520 --> 00:02:35.055
I VAGUELY RECALL
A SECRET ROOM.

00:02:35.055 --> 00:02:38.325
PEGASUS' SANCTUARY.
MAYBE IT WAS JUST
A DREAM, BUT...

00:02:38.325 --> 00:02:39.693
ONLY IF WE WERE
BOTH DREAMING.

00:02:39.693 --> 00:02:41.161
I'M STARTING TO
REMEMBER IT, TOO.

00:02:41.161 --> 00:02:42.763
PEGASUS FOUGHT
WITH BAKURA,

00:02:42.763 --> 00:02:44.431
AND THEN BAKURA'S
EVIL SPIRIT CAME OUT.

00:02:44.431 --> 00:02:45.832
BUT WHY DID WE FORGET?

00:02:45.832 --> 00:02:48.201
EVIL SPIRIT?
AARGH!

00:02:48.201 --> 00:02:50.203
YEAH. I BET HE
CAST A SPELL ON YA!

00:02:50.203 --> 00:02:52.239
WELL, WE REMEMBER NOW.
LET'S GO!

00:02:53.907 --> 00:02:55.308
HEY! WAIT UP!

00:02:58.412 --> 00:03:00.580
Pegasus: IT'S ALL OVER.

00:03:00.580 --> 00:03:02.149
EVERYTHING I'VE STRUGGLED
TO OBTAIN

00:03:02.149 --> 00:03:03.950
IS NOW BEYOND MY GRASP.

00:03:03.950 --> 00:03:06.787
KEEPING THEIR SOULS
WILL NOT SERVE ME NOW.

00:03:06.787 --> 00:03:09.623
BESIDES, I'M
A MAN OF MY WORD.

00:03:09.623 --> 00:03:12.592
AND BECAUSE OF
THE DEFEAT I SUFFERED
AT THE HANDS OF YUGI

00:03:12.592 --> 00:03:15.128
AND THE MYSTERIOUS SPIRIT
OF HIS MILLENNIUM PUZZLE,

00:03:15.128 --> 00:03:18.198
I AM DUTY-BOUND
TO FULFILL MY PLEDGE.

00:03:19.966 --> 00:03:23.203
AND SO, I RELEASE
THESE THREE SOULS.

00:03:27.541 --> 00:03:31.178
CECELIA, I'M SORRY,
BUT I HAVE FAILED YOU!

00:03:31.178 --> 00:03:33.480
MY ATTEMPT TO TAKE OVER
KAIBA CORP,

00:03:33.480 --> 00:03:36.650
MY EFFORTS TO GET ALL
THE MILLENNIUM ITEMS,
WAS ALL DONE FOR YOU.

00:03:36.650 --> 00:03:39.486
IN THE HOPES THAT I COULD
RESTORE YOU, BODY AND SOUL.

00:03:39.486 --> 00:03:41.555
Bakura: HOW SWEET.

00:03:41.555 --> 00:03:42.989
HMM? WHO'S THERE?

00:03:44.925 --> 00:03:47.561
BAKURA! I REMEMBER NOW.

00:03:47.561 --> 00:03:50.764
YOU! YOU'RE THE ONE
THAT POSSESSES
THE MILLENNIUM RING!

00:03:51.932 --> 00:03:54.401
YES. AND I INTEND TO
HAVE ALL THE ITEMS.

00:03:54.401 --> 00:03:56.303
CARE TO WAGER YOURS
ON A SHADOW GAME?

00:03:56.303 --> 00:03:58.772
I'LL GIVE YOU
A SECOND CHANCE
AT A MILLENNIUM ITEM.

00:03:58.772 --> 00:04:01.975
[CHUCKLES] WHAT YOU
COULDN'T WIN FROM YUGI,

00:04:01.975 --> 00:04:03.410
PERHAPS YOU CAN WIN
FROM ME.

00:04:04.644 --> 00:04:07.714
WHO KNOWS? IF YOU DEFEAT ME
AND CLAIM MY RING,

00:04:07.714 --> 00:04:10.784
YOUR DEEPEST DESIRES
MIGHT NOT BE BEYOND
YOUR GRASP AFTER ALL.

00:04:16.389 --> 00:04:18.258
YOUR MILLENNIUM ITEM
ALLOWS YOU TO LOOK

00:04:18.258 --> 00:04:20.026
INTO PEOPLE'S MINDS,
PEGASUS.

00:04:20.026 --> 00:04:22.262
MINE ALLOWS ME
TO SEE INTO
THEIR SOULS.

00:04:22.262 --> 00:04:24.030
I HAVE BUT TO LOOK
AT YOUR DECK,

00:04:24.030 --> 00:04:27.134
PEGASUS, AND IT
REVEALS TO ME
YOUR TRUE NATURE.

00:04:27.134 --> 00:04:29.402
THE HAPPY
LOVER CARD!

00:04:29.402 --> 00:04:32.706
IT SHOWS YOU
HAVE EXPERIENCED
THE JOYS OF LOVE.

00:04:32.706 --> 00:04:35.208
HOWEVER, THIS CARD
IS UPSIDE DOWN,

00:04:35.208 --> 00:04:38.278
WHICH MEANS
YOUR ROMANCE
ENDED IN TRAGEDY.

00:04:38.278 --> 00:04:41.815
WHAT A PITY IT IS.
WELL, THE NEXT CARD
SHOULD SHOW ME MORE

00:04:41.815 --> 00:04:44.151
ABOUT YOUR PRESENT
THAN YOUR PAST.

00:04:44.151 --> 00:04:48.088
AH! THE MASK
OF DARKNESS, EH?

00:04:48.088 --> 00:04:50.257
SO YOUR
RECENT ACTIONS WERE
ALL JUST AN EFFORT

00:04:50.257 --> 00:04:52.392
TO MASK YOUR
TRUE OBJECTIVES,

00:04:52.392 --> 00:04:54.861
OBJECTIVES
THAT CAME FROM DEEP
WITHIN YOUR HEART.

00:04:54.861 --> 00:04:57.264
WHO WOULD HAVE
THOUGHT YOU EVEN
HAD A HEART,

00:04:57.264 --> 00:04:59.666
LET ALONE ONE
SO EASILY BROKEN?

00:04:59.666 --> 00:05:01.968
QUIET! LET'S JUST
PLAY THE GAME!

00:05:01.968 --> 00:05:05.739
[CHUCKLES]
AS YOU WISH.
BUT FIRST,

00:05:05.739 --> 00:05:08.008
THERE IS ONE MORE
CARD TO BE REVEALED.

00:05:08.008 --> 00:05:10.310
DON'T YOU WANT
TO SEE YOUR FUTURE?

00:05:10.310 --> 00:05:13.446
DOMA, THE ANGEL
OF SILENCE!

00:05:13.446 --> 00:05:15.615
IT'S AN APPROPRIATE
CARD FOR YOUR FUTURE

00:05:15.615 --> 00:05:18.752
SINCE I WILL NOW
SILENCE YOU FOREVER.

00:05:18.752 --> 00:05:21.188
PREPARE YOURSELF,
MORTAL, FOR
A SHADOW GAME

00:05:21.188 --> 00:05:23.223
THE LIKES OF WHICH
YOU'VE NEVER PLAYED!

00:05:23.223 --> 00:05:24.925
[CHUCKLES]

00:05:24.925 --> 00:05:26.560
THIS MATCH
WILL BE PLAYED

00:05:26.560 --> 00:05:28.595
ON THE LANDSCAPE
OF OUR MINDS!

00:05:30.897 --> 00:05:32.299
REALLY NOW,
PEGASUS,

00:05:32.299 --> 00:05:33.533
IS THAT ALL
YOU CAN MUSTER?

00:05:34.601 --> 00:05:35.936
AH, BUT YOU'VE
BEEN FATIGUED

00:05:35.936 --> 00:05:37.904
BY YOUR SHADOW DUEL
WITH YUGI.

00:05:37.904 --> 00:05:40.440
YOUR MIND IS WEARY
WHILE MINE IS FRESH.

00:05:41.474 --> 00:05:42.876
OH!
YOU ARE DEFEATED!

00:05:42.876 --> 00:05:45.345
A RANK AMATEUR TO
ONE WHO HAS PLAYED
FOR CENTURIES.

00:05:45.345 --> 00:05:46.646
YOU'VE LIVED
FOR CENTURIES?

00:05:46.646 --> 00:05:50.016
WHAT KIND
OF CREATURE ARE YOU?

00:05:50.016 --> 00:05:53.086
I AM THE ONE WHO
WILL POSSESS ALL THE
MILLENNIUM ITEMS,

00:05:53.086 --> 00:05:55.355
AND I SHALL USE
THEIR COMBINED MIGHT

00:05:55.355 --> 00:05:57.324
TO CONQUER
THE ENTIRE WORLD!

00:05:57.324 --> 00:05:58.825
YOU HAVE LOST
THE GAME,

00:05:58.825 --> 00:06:01.661
AND THAT ENTITLES
ME TO TAKE YOUR
MILLENNIUM ITEM,

00:06:01.661 --> 00:06:04.097
THE WAY YOU MEANT
TO TAKE YUGI'S.

00:06:04.097 --> 00:06:05.966
N-NO!

00:06:05.966 --> 00:06:09.836
NO!

00:06:14.441 --> 00:06:16.009
Tristan: DID YOU
HEAR THAT SCREAM?

00:06:16.009 --> 00:06:17.410
Téa: IT CAME
FROM THE TOWER.

00:06:17.410 --> 00:06:18.445
IT SOUNDED
LIKE PEGASUS.

00:06:19.446 --> 00:06:21.147
LOOK! SOMETHING'S
HAPPENED!

00:06:22.549 --> 00:06:23.717
Yugi: IT'S HIM!

00:06:23.717 --> 00:06:25.719
[MOANS]

00:06:25.719 --> 00:06:28.021
CROQUET, WHAT
HAPPENED TO PEGASUS?

00:06:28.021 --> 00:06:31.124
IT'S NONE OF
YOUR CONCERN. HE'S
SUDDENLY TAKEN ILL.

00:06:31.124 --> 00:06:32.959
BUT WHAT ABOUT GRANDPA
AND THE OTHERS?

00:06:32.959 --> 00:06:34.928
HE PROMISED HE'D FREE
THEIR SOULS. HE PROMISED!

00:06:34.928 --> 00:06:36.563
NOT MY DEPARTMENT.

00:06:38.431 --> 00:06:40.433
HEY, DID YOU GET
A LOOK AT PEGASUS?

00:06:40.433 --> 00:06:42.669
WHO OR WHAT COULD
HAVE DONE THAT TO HIM?

00:06:42.669 --> 00:06:45.205
I DON'T KNOW.
MAYBE WE SHOULD CHECK OUT
THE TOWERS, YOU THINK?

00:06:45.205 --> 00:06:47.173
Joey: SO THIS IS WHERE
PEGASUS HANGS OUT?

00:06:47.173 --> 00:06:48.808
WHOEVER THAT WOMAN IS,
SHE SURE IS PRETTY.

00:06:48.808 --> 00:06:49.843
YEAH.

00:06:49.843 --> 00:06:51.511
Téa: HEY!

00:06:51.511 --> 00:06:52.913
WHAT'S THIS?

00:06:52.913 --> 00:06:55.081
IT SEEMS TO BE
A DIARY!

00:06:55.081 --> 00:06:56.316
HUH?

00:06:56.316 --> 00:06:58.285
MAYBE WE'LL FIND
SOMETHING IN HERE.

00:06:58.285 --> 00:06:59.953
[GASPS]

00:06:59.953 --> 00:07:02.389
IT'S ALL ABOUT PEGASUS.
LISTEN TO THIS.

00:07:02.389 --> 00:07:03.690
HE'S WRITTEN
ABOUT THAT LADY!

00:07:03.690 --> 00:07:05.191
Yugi: SHE'S EVERYWHERE!

00:07:05.191 --> 00:07:08.295
Téa: SHE SEEMS TO BE
VERY IMPORTANT TO HIM.

00:07:08.295 --> 00:07:11.665
"DARLING CECELIA,
AT LAST, I'VE FINALLY
FOUND A WAY

00:07:11.665 --> 00:07:13.099
"TO RESTORE YOU
TO THIS WORLD.

00:07:13.099 --> 00:07:14.567
"IT'S
AN ELABORATE PLAN,

00:07:14.567 --> 00:07:16.236
"BUT NOT ONE
BEYOND MY GENIUS.

00:07:16.236 --> 00:07:17.871
"IT INVOLVES
THE KAIBA CORPORATION

00:07:17.871 --> 00:07:20.073
"AND SOME ANCIENT MAGIC
I PLAN TO HARNESS

00:07:20.073 --> 00:07:22.208
WHEN I OBTAIN
MORE MILLENNIUM ITEMS."

00:07:22.208 --> 00:07:24.010
THIS COULD BE IT!
THIS MIGHT EXPLAIN

00:07:24.010 --> 00:07:25.412
WHY HE SET UP
THE TOURNAMENT

00:07:25.412 --> 00:07:27.013
AND WHY HE
WENT AFTER YUGI!

00:07:27.013 --> 00:07:28.982
AND MAYBE WHO
THIS GIRL IS.

00:07:28.982 --> 00:07:31.051
IT'S PRETTY
OBVIOUS HE'S
HUNG UP ON HER.

00:07:32.118 --> 00:07:34.387
Téa: "CECELIA,
OH, MY LOVELY..."

00:07:34.387 --> 00:07:36.056
Pegasus:
DARLING CECELIA.

00:07:36.056 --> 00:07:37.290
YOU KNOW HOW
I'VE LOVED YOU

00:07:37.290 --> 00:07:39.192
SINCE THE FIRST
MOMENT WE MET

00:07:39.192 --> 00:07:40.994
THOSE MANY YEARS AGO.

00:07:40.994 --> 00:07:42.963
I'LL NEVER
FORGET THAT DAY.

00:07:42.963 --> 00:07:46.433
IT WAS AT A PARTY
AT MY FATHER'S
COUNTRY ESTATE.

00:07:46.433 --> 00:07:49.970
IT WAS A GALA EVENT,
WITH CELEBRITIES
AND TYCOONS

00:07:49.970 --> 00:07:51.471
FROM ALL OVER
THE WORLD.

00:07:51.471 --> 00:07:54.307
ANYONE WHO WAS
ANYONE WAS THERE.

00:07:54.307 --> 00:07:59.045
BUT BY FAR, THE ONE
THAT IMPRESSED
ME MOST...WAS YOU.

00:07:59.045 --> 00:08:00.447
EVEN THOUGH WE
WERE ONLY CHILDREN,

00:08:00.447 --> 00:08:03.083
I KNEW I WAS IN LOVE.
[GIGGLES]

00:08:03.083 --> 00:08:07.020
WE WERE DRAWN TO EACH OTHER,
AND FROM THAT MOMENT ON,

00:08:07.020 --> 00:08:09.723
WE WERE INSEPARABLE,
YOU AND I.

00:08:11.458 --> 00:08:13.326
YOU INFLAMED MY PASSIONS,

00:08:13.326 --> 00:08:15.261
INSPIRED ME TO
BECOME A PAINTER.

00:08:15.261 --> 00:08:17.364
AND YOU WERE MY
FAVORITE SUBJECT.

00:08:17.364 --> 00:08:20.200
I WAS SO IN LOVE.

00:08:20.200 --> 00:08:23.303
AND JUST WHEN
I THOUGHT THINGS
COULDN'T GET ANY BETTER,

00:08:23.303 --> 00:08:28.241
YOU AGREED TO TAKE
MY HAND ONCE AGAIN,
THIS TIME, IN MARRIAGE.

00:08:28.241 --> 00:08:32.112
THAT WAS THE HAPPIEST
DAY OF MY LIFE.
BUT IT WAS CUT SHORT.

00:08:32.112 --> 00:08:34.647
FOR IT SEEMED,
JUST AS WE SAID OUR VOWS,

00:08:34.647 --> 00:08:37.650
YOU WERE STRUCK DOWN
BY A DEVASTATING DISEASE

00:08:37.650 --> 00:08:40.620
AND TAKEN FROM ME
AND THIS WORLD.

00:08:40.620 --> 00:08:43.923
IT WAS AS IF A BLOW HAD
STRUCK ME FROM THE HEAVENS.

00:08:43.923 --> 00:08:46.292
I WAS FILLED WITH SORROW.

00:08:46.292 --> 00:08:49.295
FROM THAT MOMENT ON,
I COULD NO LONGER PAINT.

00:08:49.295 --> 00:08:51.798
MY HEART GREW
BITTER AND COLD.

00:08:51.798 --> 00:08:55.735
UNABLE TO ACCEPT THE IDEA
THAT OUR LIFE TOGETHER
WAS FOREVER LOST,

00:08:55.735 --> 00:08:58.538
I DECIDED TO SCOUR
THE EARTH IN AN ATTEMPT

00:08:58.538 --> 00:09:02.776
TO FIND ANY WAY TO REACH YOU
BEYOND THIS MORTAL VEIL.

00:09:02.776 --> 00:09:06.246
MY JOURNEY EVENTUALLY
BROUGHT ME TO THE GREAT
PYRAMIDS OF EGYPT,

00:09:06.246 --> 00:09:08.715
THAT MYSTERIOUS LAND
WHOSE ANCIENT PEOPLE

00:09:08.715 --> 00:09:11.484
BELIEVED IN A LIFE
BEYOND THE HERE AND NOW--

00:09:11.484 --> 00:09:14.020
A BELIEF I WANTED
TO EMBRACE.

00:09:14.020 --> 00:09:15.922
I HAD JUST
BEGUN TO EXPLORE

00:09:15.922 --> 00:09:18.925
THAT ANCIENT CITY
WHEN FATE INTERVENED.

00:09:24.130 --> 00:09:25.165
THANK YOU.

00:09:25.165 --> 00:09:27.067
STRANGER,
HEED MY ADVICE.

00:09:27.067 --> 00:09:28.034
HUH?

00:09:28.034 --> 00:09:30.236
YOU HAVE
JOURNEYED FAR,

00:09:30.236 --> 00:09:32.705
SEEKING TO CURE
THE ACHE WITHIN
YOUR SOUL.

00:09:32.705 --> 00:09:35.375
OHH.
TAKE GREAT CARE.

00:09:35.375 --> 00:09:38.211
THE SEARCH
TO HEAL THE PAINS
OF A BROKEN HEART

00:09:38.211 --> 00:09:41.314
MIGHT LEAD TO EVEN
GREATER HEARTACHE.

00:09:41.314 --> 00:09:42.549
WAIT! HOW DO YOU KNOW?

00:09:42.549 --> 00:09:44.551
IT MATTERS NOT.
GO HOME!

00:09:44.551 --> 00:09:46.186
Pegasus: BUT I COULDN'T.

00:09:46.186 --> 00:09:48.121
I REALIZED IF HE SOMEHOW
KNEW OF MY PAIN,

00:09:48.121 --> 00:09:49.722
MAYBE HE COULD
HELP ME HEAL IT.

00:09:49.722 --> 00:09:53.827
I FOLLOWED HIM
AGAINST HIS WISHES,
OR SO I THOUGHT.

00:09:56.896 --> 00:09:58.698
ALTHOUGH THE PASSAGE
SEEMED TO LEAD

00:09:58.698 --> 00:10:01.701
TO THE BOWELS
OF THE EARTH,
STILL I FOLLOWED,

00:10:01.701 --> 00:10:04.771
AND MY FOOTSTEPS LED ME
TO A HIDDEN CRYPT,

00:10:04.771 --> 00:10:07.974
APPARENTLY BURIED BENEATH
CENTURIES OF CIVILIZATION.

00:10:09.342 --> 00:10:10.743
WHAT IS THIS PLACE?

00:10:10.743 --> 00:10:13.079
SO, YOU CHOSE NOT
TO HEED MY WARNING.

00:10:14.547 --> 00:10:15.915
[GRUNTS]

00:10:15.915 --> 00:10:18.151
Pegasus:
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
LET ME GO!

00:10:18.151 --> 00:10:21.988
I AM A GUARDIAN
OF THE MILLENNIUM ITEMS.

00:10:21.988 --> 00:10:24.290
ONCE THIS SACRED PLACE
HAS BEEN DISCOVERED,

00:10:24.290 --> 00:10:26.459
THE ONLY WAY TO LEAVE
IS TO BE CHOSEN.

00:10:26.459 --> 00:10:28.595
IT MUST BE
YOUR DESTINY.

00:10:28.595 --> 00:10:30.296
BUT HOW COULD THESE
MILLENNIUM ITEMS BE

00:10:30.296 --> 00:10:32.265
PART OF MY DESTINY?
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

00:10:32.265 --> 00:10:33.600
UHH.

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:34.834
YOU WILL NOW
BE TESTED

00:10:34.834 --> 00:10:37.904
BY THE ITEM ITSELF:
THE MILLENNIUM EYE.

00:10:40.039 --> 00:10:43.209
THE EYE ITSELF?
BUT HOW?

00:10:43.209 --> 00:10:46.513
EACH MILLENNIUM ITEM
AWAITS THE DAY
ITS FATED POSSESSOR

00:10:46.513 --> 00:10:51.284
APPEARS TO CLAIM IT
AND PUNISHES THOSE
WHO ARE UNDESERVING.

00:10:51.284 --> 00:10:52.485
PUNISHES?

00:10:52.485 --> 00:10:54.754
NOW, IF YOU
PASS ITS TEST,

