THAT DOES NOT
BODE WELL.

00:15:15.381 --> 00:15:17.350
BUT IF YOU ARE
NOT THE CRIMINAL,

00:15:17.350 --> 00:15:19.852
THEN YOU HAVE NOTHING
TO FEAR FROM MY SEARCH.

